How configure and use inputs and outputs in msp430 mcu


every port have 3 register of configuration and two mirrored register (represent the values on pins inputs/outputs)

the register to select special or normal mode is PxSEL
the register to select input or output mode is PxDir
the register to select pullup or pulldown mode is PxREN

the register to get inputs PxIN
the register to set ouputs PxOUT
